     default for new VMs (machine version 11.0+pve1 and later), as it can break
     connectivity for some guest network setups, in particular VXLAN traffic
     that leaves the host over a physical NIC. The new per-NIC 'host-tunnel'
     option allows re-enabling it explicitly.
 
